Class TabsFocusTraversalPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.FocusTraversalPolicy
      • linefit.TabsFocusTraversalPolicy

  • public class TabsFocusTraversalPolicy
extends java.awt.FocusTraversalPolicy
    A listener that is called when the user hits the tabs key that sets the order through which the options in the options menu are focused in
